# Build-context hygiene for the builder image (apps/builder/Dockerfile).
# node_modules / dist are reinstalled / rebuilt in-image for the image's
# architecture; secrets (.env) are injected at runtime via docker-compose and
# must never be baked into the image layer.
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.turbo
**/*.tsbuildinfo
**/*.log
.git
.env
.env.*
.claude
